comment: Horford (ATL) legally guards Lopez (BKN) as he cuts through the lane. Contact does not affect his FOM.
Millsap (ATL) sets the screen on Jack (BKN) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Johnson (BKN) has a hand on Millsap's (ATL) back with a bent elbow.
Lopez (BKN) is in the paint for longer than 3 seconds.
Williams (BKN) commits a take foul on Korver (ATL).
Lopez (BKN) commits a take foul on Bazemore (ATL).
